text: Danna Maria García Osuna (born 4 February 1978) is a Colombian actress and model. She was born in Medellín. She is best known for her roles in telenovelas. Her most notable credits include Pasión de Gavilanes, Qué bonito amor and El Señor de los Cielos. In March 2020, during the 2019–20 coronavirus pandemic, García tested positive for COVID-19. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1978 births Category:Living people Category:Colombian television actors Category:Actors from Medellín Category:Colombian models
